HEADWORD: Cream-faced
<hw>Cream"-faced`</hw> <pr>(kr?m"f?st`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>White
or pale, as the effect of fear, or as the natural complexion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou <qex>cream-faced</qex> loon.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

